trans-unit.source: Represents the compiler for workflows that are developed using C# or Visual Basic code and/or XAML markup.
trans-unit.target: 表示工作流程的編譯器，這些工作流程是使用 C# 或 Visual Basic 程式碼和/或 XAML 標記所開發的。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates how to create a new instance of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowCompiler> class and run the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowCompiler.Compile%2A> method.

trans-unit.source: The code also creates a new instance of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowCompilerParameters> class and sets some of its values.
trans-unit.target: 程式碼也會建立 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowCompilerParameters> 類別的新執行個體，並設定它的某些值。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowCompilerParameters" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowCompilerParameters" />。

trans-unit.source: A string array that contains the paths to the files to compile.
trans-unit.target: 字串陣列，包含要編譯之檔案的路徑。

trans-unit.source: These files can be either code files (such as .vb or .cs) or workflow markup files.
trans-unit.target: 這些檔案可以是程式碼檔案 (例如 .vb 或 .cs) 或工作流程標記檔案。

trans-unit.source: Workflow markup files must have an .xoml extension to be recognized by the compiler.
trans-unit.target: 工作流程標記檔案的副檔名必須是編譯器可辨識的 .xoml 副檔名。

trans-unit.source: Compiles a list of workflows contained in the files that are passed as parameters based on the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowCompilerParameters" />.
trans-unit.target: 編譯包含在檔案中的工作流程清單，這些工作流程會根據 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowCompilerParameters" /> 當做參數傳遞。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowCompilerResults" /> representing the results of the operation.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowCompilerResults" />，表示作業的結果。
